  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Shelter and Essential Household Services (NFI) Assistance for Internally Displaced Persons in Masisi Territory, North Kivu</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of IOM&apos;s actions will be to improve the living conditions of the people affected by the conflict in North Kivu by rapidly responding to their needs for shelter and essential household items (NFIs). The intervention strategy developed under this CERF allocation will be implemented in Masisi territory in North Kivu province.</narrative>
  </description>
